description: Parq is a commandline tool for multiple OS for inspecting Apache Parquet files. This tools gives a simple data inspector which lists out the columns found in a Parquet data set and the data values for those columns.
summary: Parq is a .NET runtime (written for Windows but will run elsewhere) that brings tooling for inspecting Parquet files to developers.
author: Andy Cross,  Richard Conway,  Ivan Gavryliuk
